{"tid":2119008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：美國疫情可能變壞　民眾應戴口罩","createTime":"2020-07-22T00:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T01:49:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"590849e064d266604c498ce2ec0c67516c03d9a1","tid":2119008,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/07/22/2528358_8a33fc29e1ef6a46d8788542edecb1aa_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F07%2F22%2F2528358_8a33fc29e1ef6a46d8788542edecb1aa_320.jpg&h=8114c103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總統特朗普周二出席白宮疫情發布會時表示，美國的新冠病毒疫情可能進一步惡化，其後才可能好轉。<br />\n<br />\n根據約翰霍普金斯大學統計，美國確診人數累積至逾380萬人，死亡人數超過14.1萬。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普事隔多月首次再度出席疫情發布會，他指出，美國多個州政府領袖正努力應對疫情，聯邦政府也致力提供醫療設備，幫助醫護人員救治病人。他強調，不會要求全國封城，因為美國難以承受封鎖的後果，封城會對經濟造成重大災難。同時，美國對疫情的了解加深，也有足夠的醫療器材及治療方案。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普促請美國民眾佩戴口罩，以防止病毒擴散。對於檢測工作，特朗普強調美國是全球病毒檢測量最多的國家，已經進行近5000萬人次檢測。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普稱，有信心新冠病毒最終會消失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2528358/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2528358%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtBxmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=ac10329e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2528358/</a>"},{"pid":"e117bdf98fcbb6f5ca9dea4663e7d94985226356","tid":2119008,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:58:18.000Z","msg":"仲以為係天氣開始轉涼了潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f47d7e695d23645fe7d569c19e378a5aae01f71","tid":2119008,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"重視病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bb0572dc198aca6854b0d76167ac44dd0183df","tid":2119008,"uid":37502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"cited